@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cnieqr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.13 - v2 + 0.68)))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.89) * (v1 + 0.76 - tmp + 0.06)) / wp.sin(v1))
    tmp = (v0 / wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.14)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.94)) * (wp.sin(v2 + 0.36) - wp.sin(tmp + 0.50)))
    v1 = (v0 + wp.cos(0.17))
    tmp = wp.abs(v0)
    v0 = wp.sin((v1 * tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
